{"tid":1938764,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎係我隔離","createTime":"2020-03-22T18:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T19:19:54.000Z","uid":347812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e8d1c3929c046a4d9bff8f58f05f095618622e8","tid":1938764,"uid":347812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T18:22:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://wars.vote4.hk/cases/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwars.vote4.hk%2Fcases%2F&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdLXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=41ff8cd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://wars.vote4.hk/cases/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n推介各位用下呢個網站<br />\n點解咁好用都唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地班香港人知唔知武漢肺炎總有一個係左近<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫封關叫十世都唔封<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班高官又盲又聾又冇腦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲想靠政府？不了 我選擇靠自己</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個網站入面好詳細提供武漢肺炎係香港既情況同資訊<br />\n只要打地方名就搵到自己附近有冇確診者經過或居住既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入面亦有關於抗疫既資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抗爭之餘都要小心身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全城幫手推</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P2uBBmw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP2uBBmw.png&h=cb365012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jn3yDzS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJn3yDzS.png&h=8015d574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ebf95454f4088322459025a4b15ffed7a920e2a","tid":1938764,"uid":347812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T18:23:03.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"1697ad204442bb163ba8c937d2911f9ed379771f","tid":1938764,"uid":347812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T18:23:13.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"c074265e247deb8c83932bd0267912b44c4f13e0","tid":1938764,"uid":347812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T18:23:23.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"b089dc69f4bd007585c8d7e5613d5574aa2fdbc9","tid":1938764,"uid":347812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T18:23:33.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"3eec656e5fd08c5a38292181c59f504618030c6f","tid":1938764,"uid":347812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T18:23:44.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"3694a605007d17e29647b9442c000d36989b409d","tid":1938764,"uid":347812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T18:23:54.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"27ca51cef6f35f11dd6ec884a5bfe98eebef52e9","tid":1938764,"uid":347812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T18:24:04.000Z","msg":"推7"},{"pid":"1e37aa81bfa8d6f22bca15254adda309d1193023","tid":1938764,"uid":347812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T18:24:14.000Z","msg":"推8"},{"pid":"23071a150362f4df6f785b443541cde2ace40c92","tid":1938764,"uid":347812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T18:24:24.000Z","msg":"推9"},{"pid":"9ed93367647bc6c15f489b84a1e70e8334a58f0c","tid":1938764,"uid":347812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T18:24:35.000Z","msg":"推10"},{"pid":"cdf565642e193d39fab82081a9c2e6f083d48479","tid":1938764,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T19:19:54.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n我去過其中一個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as